item.title: CVE-2022-1562|2024-08-03T00:10:03.556Z -- unknown -- enable%20svg
item.description: The Enable SVG WordPress plugin before 1.4.0 does not sanitise uploaded SVG files, which could allow users with a role as low as Author to upload a malicious SVG containing XSS payloads
